    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s looking for a brand-new home! It\u2019s been a super reliable car for me and still runs like a dream. It\u2019s been really well-loved and maintained over the years, so it\u2019s in great shape and ready for plenty more adventures. If you're looking for a solid, comfy vehicle that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
