      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, a quintessential analog performer featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a functional M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure long-term structural rigidity. The suspension remains tight with upgraded bushings and Bilstein dampers, providing excellent turn-in and dampening characteristics. While the exterior shows minor road-wear consistent with a well-loved driver, the powertrain and drivetrain are in excellent health, offering a visceral 8,000 RPM redline experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean interior. Runs well. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 31500.0,
