    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of luxury and dependability. The exterior maintains a deep, lustrous finish that catches the light beautifully, showing only the minor, expected signs of careful road use consistent with its age. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the premium upholstery remains supple and clean, and every electronic feature\u2014from the intuitive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car has been treated with the utmost respect. It comes with a consistent service history, ensuring the engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts seamlessly through every gear. From the responsive handling to the crisp premium audio system, this car provides a driving experience that feels both refined and assured. It is a reliable, well-cared-for example that is ready for its next chapter and many more miles of enjoyment.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Boasting a comprehensive service history and exceptional mechanical integrity, it delivers a refined driving experience characterized by both performance and consistency. The interior remains in impressive condition, reflecting a high standard of ownership and care. We invite serious inquiries to inspect this well-appointed example of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 34500.0,
