      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable, clean inside and out, and it still handles like a dream! It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants a dependable car without the 'brand new' price tag. I've taken great care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a good home. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
