    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist\u2019s dream, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 with its signature 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from the M-specific subframe and aluminum suspension components. Power is delivered through a lightning-fast M-DCT dual-clutch transmission and managed by the M Variable Differential Lock for optimal corner-exit traction. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the mechanical integrity of this high-revving powerhouse. Finished in a driver-focused spec, it delivers an uncompromising analog experience with modern precision.",
